title: Great Price- Spacious 1 Bed- Walk in Closet- Fitness Center
posting_body: ['APARTMENT FEATURES-', 'Floor to Ceiling Windows', 'Large Walk in Closet', 'Generous Floor Plan', 'Individually Controlled Heat and AC', 'Formal, Separate Dining Areas', 'Complimentary Storage Lockers', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES-', '48th Floor Fitness Center', 'Year Round Sunroom with Retractable Skylight', 'Full Time, Door Staff', 'On-Site Management and Maintenance', 'Bike Storage', 'Indoor Pedway Access to the Metra, Shopping and Restaurants', 'Renovated Laundry Room', 'Valet Parking Available', 'Call or Email to schedule a tour!', 'We are available 7 days a week.', 'Downtown Apartment Company LLC', '730 N Wells Chicago, IL 60654', '312-772-3929', 'REF#34', 'Pictures are representative samples of the advertised unit.', 'In some cases, the actual units you tour may vary from the pictures based on the specific floor plan available.', 'Availability and prices are subject to change (and often do change daily).', 'Addresses, cross-streets or other geographic information, if provided, is intended to provide a general location of the advertised unit only; you should not rely on any address provided in this advertisement as an exact location of the unit.', 'Please contact us for exact addresses.', 'Units are leased unfurnished unless otherwise specified.', '12-month minimum lease term is standard for most units, but minimum term varies.', 'Equal housing opportunity.']
